content_request: donne moi le volume d'appels vers Orange et Free

-- Requête SQL envoyée :

SELECT
    daily_voix.year AS year,
    daily_voix.month AS month,
    SUM(daily_voix.Orange) AS volume_appels_orange,
    SUM(daily_voix.Free) AS volume_appels_free
FROM
    daily_voix
WHERE daily_voix.year = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE())
GROUP BY
    daily_voix.year,
    daily_voix.month;
